{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1c927ef40c","title":"对纺织部关于经纬纺织机器厂盲日施工造成严重问题的检讨的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bf1720c091","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":23,"articleId":"1c927ef40c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"1e275c0395","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1c927ef40c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周思来。朱，指朱德。陈，指陈云，当时任政务院副总理兼财政经济委员会主任。富春，即季富春，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任、中央人民政府节约检查委员会副主任。"},{"id":"bcdd5ff339","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1c927ef40c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指纺织工业部1952年1月21日给毛泽东并中央的检讨报告中所讲的部属新建经纬纺织机器制造厂因盲目施工造成严重问题一事。报告说，该厂自1951年5月施工，现已完成建筑工作总量的43%，经检查，主要的机工厂房，由于勘察设计不周，施工不善，工程落成时，大梁出现裂缝，280根柱子发生不平衡下沉6分至5寸的严重现象。"}],"contents":[{"id":"27aede8447","type":"title","text":"对纺织部关于经纬纺织机器厂青日施工造成严重问题的检讨的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1c927ef40c"},{"id":"1e275c0395","type":"paragraph","text":"周、朱、陈、富春阅。此事值得注意。如此盲目施工，危险极大。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1c927ef40c"},{"id":"bcdd5ff339","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1c927ef40c"},{"id":"7c867f0175","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿三日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1c927ef40c"}],"page":{"id":"a595ded0b7","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"1c927ef40c","start":290,"end":290}}}},"__N_SSG":true}